Requires:         R-CRAN-ape 
Requires:         R-CRAN-distory 
Requires:         R-CRAN-ggplot2 

%description
A non-parametric method for identifying potential outlying observations in
a collection of phylogenetic trees based on the methods of Owen and Provan
(2011). Such discordant trees may indicate problems with sequence
annotation or tree reconstruction, or they may represent interesting
biological phenomena, such as horizontal gene transfers.

